   description	: "4.3.4 Restricted Groups Remote Desktop Users: None"
   info			: "With Restricted Groups enabled, the operating system will evaluate local group membership on boot and when group policy refreshes. Members in the 'Restricted Groups' policy are compared against the actual, current group membership. If the accounts listed in the policy are not in the group, they are added. Conversely, if an account is in the group but not in the policy, it is removed."
